These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 5

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-5-1::.
City: liverpool, hamburg
There 2 different types of food: grapefruit, cranberry
1. the person traveling to hamburg is somewhere to the left of the person eating grapefruit##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |
| City           | hamburg | liverpool |
| Food   | cranberry     | grapefruit  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-5-2::.
House: victorian, townhouse
There 2 different types of food: cabbage, grapes
1. the person eating cabbage is somewhere to the left of the victorian house##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1     |     2     |
| House         | townhouse   | victorian      |
| Food   | cabbage | grapes |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-5-3::.
City: venice, paris
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: game, ritmeester
1. the person traveling to venice is somewhere to the right of the game-smoker##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |   2    |
| City   | paris | venice    |
| Cigar     | game | ritmeester |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-5-4::.
There are 2 different favourite colors: red, light-blue
