 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-5-6::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: comedy, sports
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: august, april
1. the person watching comedy movies is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in august##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |        2        |
| Movie-Genre   | sports  | comedy     |
| Birthday        | august | april |

 #################################

 
