.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-5-10::.
There are 2 different nationalities: indonesian, malaysian
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: disaster, superhero
1. the person watching superhero movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching disaster movies##5
2. the indonesian is somewhere to the right of the malaysian##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |
| Nationality   | malaysian | indonesian |
| Movie-Genre     | superhero   | disaster    |

